<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Does the pleasure of reading appeal to you? Do you want to master the craft of interpreting and analyzing texts? The English major prepares students with critical thinking, clear and effective writing, research skills, and the ability to interpret and analyze textual data. From film to graphic novels to poetry, and more, our courses cast a wide net to expand and deepen our understanding of what counts as “English literature.”</p>
